{"tid":914671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<台灣玩完>國民黨候選人：大陸人來台應該4年就取得身份證投票","createTime":"2018-11-24T13:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T15:50:04.000Z","uid":144372,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"579b1575ee44bfb06d4dcf76f2a2e9681f4a2433","tid":914671,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180801/1225249.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180801%2F1225249.htm&d=Iu09UzP52py%2B%2B02xRqOubXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=91b39c34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180801/1225249.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n根據現行法律規定，外籍配偶適用的是國籍法、入出國及移民法，內容規定需居留3年、定居1年，合計滿4年以上，方可取得台灣身分證；大陸配偶則適用兩岸人民關係條例，內容明定要居留4年、定居2年，合計滿6年，才能得到台灣身分證。也就是說，大陸配偶想要取得台灣身分證，足足要比外配多上2年的時間。<br />\n<br />\n外籍配偶與大陸配偶因為適用的法律不同，入台到入籍取得身分證的時間也不同。對此，丁守中表示，過去自己在立法院曾提案，質疑陸配公民權為何要拖到六年才能成為「國民」？痛批民進黨執政不力，應該要有一套標準，陸配、外配一視同仁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 陸配6年才能成為「國民」　丁守中推4年就該拿到身分證 | ETtoday政治 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180801/1225249.htm#ixzz5XmDpV5IB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180801%2F1225249.htm%23ixzz5XmDpV5IB&d=Iu09UzP52py%2B%2B02xRqOubXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3497cba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180801/1225249.htm#ixzz5XmDpV5IB</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"faeb786d535cba9f07f8db6ad8854b12301c2200","tid":914671,"uid":41524,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"和平統一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b93462c0fc9f755df8ac8019295af7f7db6652","tid":914671,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"好好睇清楚香港人落難時台灣人嘅咀臉，等時香港獨立後一定要對台灣人有仇報仇!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/911295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h